result.formatted_address: 道, Lin Fa Kung Temple, Tai Hang, Hong Kong
result.name: Bond Bar And Restaurant

reviews.text: The atmosphere is nice. Food is not superb but didn’t disappoint us. My friends loved the short ribs. I liked the steak and the pasta on cheese wheel. Their other pastas are good too. Will come here again.

Lunch menu had good choices. Food was OK. (Fish was a bit overcooked but still nice) 
Service good and friendly.
Avocado toast has a very watery cole slaw that was unexpected. Burrata pork was okay. Great service and atmosphere though.
Nice foods, good service
Everything was good with the hotel except the food, we tried all the outlets but nothing was impressive!

result.adr_address: 98 Tung Lo Wan Rd, Causeway Bay, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 98 Tung Lo Wan Rd, Causeway Bay, Hong Kong
result.name: Little Tai Hang

reviews.text: What draws me to this hotel is its neighborhood, which is happening as we speak.  Within minutes of walking distance are an increasing number of good restaurants and relaxing bars that locals frequent.  The feeling of living among the locals without being away from the excitement of a great city that offers great things from many cultures.  Causeway Bay is only a leisure 10 minutes walk.  Supermarket is around the corner if you happen to stay at a room with a kitchen, which is a great way to save money.

Location is decent, close to the MTR and supermarkets.  New facility, decent gym.
Beds are however small and lumpy. For the price they are asking, you’d expect a much better bed. 
Don’t try to cook anything with even the slightest oil, the ventilation is ineffective and windows do not open even a tad.
The hotel is still very new, furnishing and equipment used seems top notch. The kids loved the special bath tub. The view was great. Room size is generous for Hong Kong. Nothing to complain about.
Excellent small hotel / serviced apartment. Great for longer stays. Location is very good.
I have been living here for a quite a long time. Nice location but horrible quality of service and house keeper. Do not recommend to stay here for too long. Maybe okay for a short trip.
